    "en": "Tracks first-team head coaches or interim head coaches in the top divisions of England, Spain, Germany, Italy, and France. The primary scope counts coaches whose association was an AFC member at the time of the spell; a broader boundary scope also lists Turkish and Israeli UEFA-association cases that are often discussed in geographic Asian contexts."
  },
  "scope_note": {
